    "content": "<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 16.8667px; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 16.8667px; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #236fa1; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; text-decoration-line: underline; color: #236fa1; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1313704627670441984\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">《京东开放平台个人/个体店个护健康品类销售激励政策》</a></span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 16.8667px; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">明确了</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">达成12月销售GMV环比11月增长阶梯目标要求，且满足参与对象限定条件，方可享受对应阶梯折扣<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #236fa1;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000;\">。</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 16.8667px; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】&nbsp;<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #236fa1; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; text-decoration-line: underline; color: #236fa1; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1312972494889787392\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">《京东开放平台保证金管理规则》</a></span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 16.8667px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #236fa1;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;①针对部分表述进行优化；②调整保证金缴纳及退还相关规则。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 16.8667px; font-family: 等线;\"