in; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;①时间节奏：预热期 2025年12月6日00:00:00-2025年12月7日23:59:59；活动期 2025年12月8日00:00:00-2025年12月14日23:59:59。②玩法：打标、跨店满减、官方直降。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 16.8667px; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span></strong><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】&nbsp;<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; text-decoration-line: none; color: #3768fa; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1313744445082148864\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #236fa1; text-decoration-line: underline;\">《京东开放平台服务延迟报备规则》</span></a></span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 16.8667px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #236fa1;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">核心内容：</span></strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000;\">①将&ldquo;物流停运&rdquo;原因拆分为&ldquo;自然灾害/恶劣天气&rdquo;、&ldquo;国家重大会议/活动&rdquo;两个报备原因。② 优化报备路径。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 16.8667px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">【规则生效】</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 29.3333px; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #236fa1;\"><a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; text-decoration-line: underline; color: #236fa1; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1311235703371833344\">《京东开放平台标错类事件处理标准》</a></span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 29.3333px; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①调整标错类事件的定义，对&ldquo;标错价&rdquo;细化定义；②更新标错类事件报备流程及路径；③调整标错类时间处理时效要求；④调整处理措施。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 29.3333px; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span styl